node.text: BBQ never started as a way to be the best women pitmasters, that just happened… We never set out to be a pioneer. Like we’ve always said, our Dad was just trying to teach us how to make it in the world. But that doesn’t mean we don’t love supporting women in whatever their goals are. Thank you to the @kcwoso team for celebrating Juneteenth with us!!

node.title: The KC National Women's Soccer League Celebrates Juneteenth with Jones BBQ

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jones Bar-B-Q Kansas City on August 07, 2021. May be an image of food.

node.text: Don’t forget, we’ll be back to our normal hours starting Tuesday, August 10! Catch us smoking up all the meats from 11 AM to 3 PM… ish.⁠

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jones Bar-B-Q Kansas City on August 05, 2021. May be an image of food and indoor.

node.text: We wanna see how you use the best BBQ sauce in town!! Tag us @jonesbbqkc to be featured.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jones Bar-B-Q Kansas City on August 03, 2021. May be an image of food.

node.text: Oops, we didn’t mean to make you drool! It’s just a natural side-effect of our scrumptious plates. 🤤⁠

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jones Bar-B-Q Kansas City on July 31, 2021. May be an image of food.

node.text: Feeling sauce-y? Good thing, we’ve got lots. Tell us, what’s your go-to: sweet and tangy or hot and spicy! 👇

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jones Bar-B-Q Kansas City on July 29, 2021. May be an image of indoor.

node.text: While we love to cook and smoke our meats, we don't love to cook ourselves in this HOT HEAT! 🔥That being said, we will be CLOSED today, July 29th due to extreme temperatures. No fear though, our vending machine is stocked with your favorites. Thank you for understanding ❤️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jones Bar-B-Q Kansas City on July 27, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, outdoors and text that says 'JONES BAR-B-Q'.

node.text:
Food is for feeding your stomach. BBQ is for feeding your soul. Why else would they call it soul food? Instagram 📸: @klee_yo⁠
⁠
P.S. We will be closing at 1:30 p.m. this week due to the extreme heat. Regular hours will resume next week, but until then our refrigerated vending machine will continue to be restocked daily!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jones Bar-B-Q Kansas City on July 24, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, indoor and text that says 'IONES JONES KARSAS CITY DON'T FORGET TO TRY OUR SAUCES ۲YY JONES BAR-B-Q Pleaeu sanitizing wipe selecting before tem JONES STOCKE BAR-B-Q'.

node.text: Your search is over! Our BBQ is not only available made-to-order, but our vending machine means that you never have to go looking for BBQ open late. It’s restocked daily and refrigerated to keep everything fresh and delicious.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jones Bar-B-Q Kansas City on July 22, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text.

node.text: Not saying we’re better or anything, but we sure are the best in frat houses all over the country now that we’ve been featured on @barstoolsports. Watching @lilsasquatch666  and @adamferrone dig in to our ribs made us realize how much we don’t miss college. Thanks for coming and spending some time with us! Check out the full video at the link in our bio or at the @barstoolsports page.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jones Bar-B-Q Kansas City on July 20, 2021. May be an image of food.

node.text: BACK OPEN! Get here early to get a plate of our mouthwatering barbecue!⁠ 😍

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jones Bar-B-Q Kansas City on July 17, 2021. May be an image of 3 people, people standing and outdoors.

node.text: Our Juneteenth sure was special this year when the @kcwoso team came by and celebrated with us! Tune in to their next game on Sunday at 6 pm, where they’ll be facing off against the Washington Spirits. And make it a watch party with our bottled sauce at home, or place an order for pickup on Saturday!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jones Bar-B-Q Kansas City on July 15, 2021. May be an image of food.

node.text: Want to put a finishing touch on any of your meats, BBQ or not? Our sauce works as a perfect seasoning and flavor enhancer. So don’t hold back, lather it on thick! Get it delivered straight to your house by checking out our shop, link in bio.

node.text: Everybody who came to the @kcbbqfest gets an A+ from us! We absolutely loved seeing all you BBQ fans out at Arrowhead. Video courtesy of @KCBBQFest.
